	\param[in]	k		Spectral samples indexes vector size.
	
	
	\param[out]	yR		DFT spectral samples real part vector pointer 
						corresponds to indexes `ind`.
						Vector size is `[k x 1]`.
						Memory must be allocated.
						
	
